    <h2>Apps that Cross Platforms</h2>
    <p>A Meteor developer can launch cross-platform mobile apps with the same web language. We brought this idea to life by crafting a plausible use-case and delivering content-first design & elegant engineering. Our objective was to showcase functionality while also communicating a relatable narrative.</p>
    <p>We started with "Local Market", a mock grocery store in search of deeper customer engagement. Stores that sell ingredients can further engage customers in the adjacent steps of making food like discovery or preparation. We focussed on recipe discovery because the aspirational aspects of cooking easily segue into social sharing. The Local Market app features curated recipes made with ingredients found at the grocer. These   handsome recipes can be the topic of conversation with other customers in the app or on Twitter.</p>
  </div>
</div>

